                        Note that special terms apply to some services offered on SportWiz, like rules for particular contests or sweepstakes or other features or activities.<br />
                        These terms are posted in connection with the applicable service. Any such terms are in addition to these terms of use, and in the event of a conflict, prevail over these terms of use.

                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--================Terms END =================-->

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>



@section Scripts {
    @{await Html.RenderPartialAsync("_ValidationScriptsPartial");}
}